certificateDeclarationStandIn.title = Confirm the certificate
certificateDeclarationStandIn.caption = Submit a certificate
certificateDeclarationStandIn.heading = Confirm the certificate
certificateDeclarationStandIn.paragraph1 = It is your responsibility to make sure the SAO has reviewed and approved everything before you submit.
certificateDeclarationStandIn.paragraph2 = By submitting this certificate, you confirm that:
